txt.en: Assist the Gabil'akkâ and open up Gundabad
Talk to Prince Ingór at Maergrind in Gundabad
Prince Ingór can be found at Maergrind, the The Noble Gate of Máttugard in Gundabad.\n\nYou have been summoned by Prince Ingór to Gundabad.

Assist the Gabil'akkâ and break through the icy wall blocking the entrance to Gundabad.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>You can gain entrance to Gundabad by advancing the Legacy of Durin storyline through 'Chapter 5.2: Breaking Through.'</rgb>

You have been summoned by those who seek to reclaim Gundabad.

You should meet at Máttugard in Gundabad as soon as you are able.

<rgb=#FF0000>You can gain entrance to Gundabad by advancing the Legacy of Durin storyline through 'Chapter 5.2: Breaking Through.'</rgb>
'Ah, there you are! As you can see, we have broken through the gates, [placeholder]. The Zhélruka will soon have their reward! Gundabad will soon be ours again!'
